  "texts": [
    "The keywords included in this cluster are \"computational linguistics\", \"deep learning\", \"knowledge management\", \"language model\", \"learning algorithms\", and \"natural language processing systems\".",
    "These keywords relate to behavioral research, computational linguistics, and machine learning algorithms that are used to create and improve GenAI systems.",
    "The third (blue) cluster is characterised by the frequent use of eight categories.",
    "The most frequently occurring categories are \"decision making\", \"generative adversarial networks\", \"information analysis\", \"learning systems\", \"statistics\" and \"data mining\".",
    "This cluster describes the utilisation of GenAI for the analysis of large data sets, forecasting and the identification of patterns."
  ]
}